        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the data bus pins to the specified data value. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>data</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The 8-bit data value to set on the data bus</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
This function will set the data bus pins (D0-D7) to the corresponding bits of the data value. It will iterate through each bit of the data byte and set the corresponding data pin HIGH or LOW based on the value of that bit. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
